name: About Us and Our Tickets: Who are we?
description:
Nets Courtside - Brooklyn Tickets
DDKD Partners - Building Long Term Business Relationships

Who we are? Brooklyn Nets Season Ticket Holders.

Disclaimer: No affiliation with the Brooklyn Nets or the NBA.

Your Destination for VIP Tickets at Barclays Center:

-Excellent Customer Service - 24/7
-Fast Free Delivery Via Email
-Tickets for Nets Game are Available up to 1 Hour Before TipOff
-Avoid StubHub Fees
-Our Prices are Negotiable for Repeat Customers Only
-We do not accept returns or exchanges unless a game is cancelled


OUR VIP TICKETS INCLUDE THE FOLLOWING BENEFITS:
Loaded Ticket Complimentary Food and Non Alcoholic Beverages at at the permanent concession stands on the concourse, available from 90 minutes before tip-off until 8 minutes remain in the 4th quarter. Concession stands include Junior's, Blue Marble & More.

Concierge Service

VIP ACCESS North - South Club/Premium Lounge within Barclays Center

10% Discount at the Nets Store in Barclays Center

Contact Us Directly or View Available Games On Our Purchasing Site, Nets Ticket Exchange or StubHub.com

We guarantee same day delivery of electronic tickets during the season.

Email us for package deals!

*Buy 4 games to receive a $100 discount on your order! USE Code: "NETSFAN" at checkout*
